overview: Tim Dowling is COO of Onelogin. Prior to OneLogin Tim was VP and GM of McAfee Secure, McAfee’s first SaaS business, where he grew revenues from $0 to over $50M run-rate in under 24 months. He was CEO of Pure Networks, acquired by Cisco and was with Intel for 14 years where lead Intel’s internet initiatives prior to joining the start up world. Tim lives in San Francisco. Tim is also a private investor with interests in several startups.
